Federation_Profile_object.remarks: u003cpu003eDear Priya:u0026nbsp;u0026nbsp;u003c/pu003ennu003cpu003eI have reviewed the task/family data.u0026nbsp; As discussed on the phone, each section needs some more probing and correct data.u0026nbsp; Please see my comments below. These comments are valid for all families uploaded so far.u0026nbsp; Let me know if you need any help.u0026nbsp;u003c/pu003ennu003colu003entu003cliu003eu003cstrongu003eProfileu003c/strongu003eu0026nbsp;u0026ndash; it is overall ok but following needs to be clarified/improved:u003c/liu003enu003c/olu003ennu003culu003entu003cliu003eIs this female headed household?u0026nbsp; She has a husband who is earning.u003c/liu003entu003cliu003eQ no 20 on detailed profile of each member, please explain properly nature of job for each member.u0026nbsp; Instead of u0026ldquo;privateu0026rdquo; write exactly the job title and name of company.u003c/liu003entu003cliu003eFor Hemath members, clarify it is income from trade source and write exactly what is their trade and not u0026ldquo;From Hemathu0026rdquo;u003c/liu003entu003cliu003eAlso since most of them are also receiving govt assistance as part of migration, that should be included in u0026ldquo;other incomeu0026rdquo; and explained in the observations.u003c/liu003entu003cliu003eQ no govt programs, include all benefits that member families are receiving from the govt.u003c/liu003entu003cliu003eQ. on Education u0026ndash; is it true that both husband and wife are not educated even upto 6th standard?u003c/liu003entu003cliu003eQ on Migration u0026ndash; explain it a bit u0026ndash; migrated due to conflict in Kashmir/terrorism.u003c/liu003entu003cliu003eWealth rank u0026ndash; could you please let me know how you are deciding on V.Poor, Poor, Medium Poor and Rich. Is this family very poor?u003c/liu003enu003c/ulu003ennu003cpu003eu003cstrongu003e2.u0026nbsp; u0026nbsp; u0026nbsp; Assetsu0026nbsp;u003c/strongu003eu0026ndash; check all assets.u003c/pu003ennu003culu003entu003cliu003eFor this family, smartphone is shown as u0026ldquo;nou0026rdquo; but they have washing machine, and other gadgets.u003c/liu003entu003cliu003eUnder advanced labor, please say nou003c/liu003entu003cliu003eCheck all other assets as wellu003c/liu003enu003c/ulu003ennu003cpu003e3.u0026nbsp;u003cstrongu003eGoalsu0026nbsp;u003c/strongu003eu0026ndash; goals need to be explained properly and have to be specific to the family.u0026nbsp; I have explained this on the phone. The goal has to be for next 2 to 3 years and should be specific, measurable, realistic and timebound.u0026nbsp; Have a good discussion with them on their family goals.u003c/pu003ennu003cpu003eu003cstrongu003e4.u0026nbsp; u0026nbsp;Savingsu0026nbsp;u003c/strongu003eu0026ndash; there is no data. Please probe them into this and find out how much do they save per month or have some fixed savings.u003c/pu003ennu003cpu003eu003cstrongu003e5.u0026nbsp; Loansu0026nbsp;u003c/strongu003eu0026ndash; check out all sources of loans. Sometime, families borrow from their parents, siblings, friends and neighbors.u0026nbsp; How did they buy the motorbike?u0026nbsp; Who paid for it?u0026nbsp; Probe into all loansu003c/pu003ennu003cpu003eu003cstrongu003e6. Incomeu0026nbsp;u003c/strongu003eu0026ndash; Income section needs proper explanation and captured in proper format eg.u003c/pu003ennu003culu003entu003cliu003eArchanau0026rsquo;s income is not fixed income.u0026nbsp; It is income from trade and can vary from year to year depending on what she produces.u003c/liu003entu003cliu003eAnilu0026rsquo;s income needs to be shown as monthly income u0026ndash; how much does he make on a monthly basis and how many months does he work?u003c/liu003entu003cliu003eIf they are getting any other income, it should be shown in correct heading.u003c/liu003enu003c/ulu003ennu003cpu003eu003cstrongu003e7.u0026nbsp; Expenditureu0026nbsp;u003c/strongu003esection needs to be properly discussed and captured:u003c/pu003ennu003culu003entu003cliu003eMotor bike repair is shown monthly u0026ndash; that seems incorrect. May be it is petrol cost u0026ndash; please check. Is it true that their motorbike cost is 50% of total expenses u0026ndash; seems incorrect to me.u003c/liu003entu003cliu003eOther expense need to be recorded properly e.g. clothing, entertainment, electricity, etcu003c/liu003entu003cliu003eSocial and cultural expenses are an important part of our lives u0026ndash; please discuss and find out from each family.u003c/liu003entu003cliu003eThere are other expenses such as smoking, drinking or other unnecessary expenses and those need to be recorded properlyu003c/liu003entu003cliu003eThis family earns close to 2lakhs per month, spends 60,000 u0026ndash; where is rest of the income going?u0026nbsp;u003c/liu003enu003c/ulu003ennu003cpu003eu003cstrongu003e8.u0026nbsp; Challengesu003c/strongu003eu0026nbsp;u0026ndash; not captured properly. What does this mean u0026ldquo;shortage of day to day needsu0026rdquo;???u0026nbsp; they are not showing any needs and should have much more money in their pocket. Ask them for real challenges they are facing u0026ndash; again will be specific to each family and how they will like to resolve those challenges?u003c/pu003ennu003cpu003eu003cstrongu003e9. Action planu0026nbsp;u003c/strongu003eu0026ndash; missing u0026ndash; they need to commit to actions for next 6 to 12 months to overcome their challenges and improve their family development.u003c/pu003ennu003cpu003eu003cstrongu003e10.u0026nbsp; u0026nbsp;Observationsu0026nbsp;u003c/strongu003eThere is no story about this family.u0026nbsp; The observations should include the following:u003c/pu003ennu003culu003entu003cliu003eBackground about the family u0026ndash; whether they are young, old, disabled, whatever the family structure is u0026ndash; some sense of who they are.u0026nbsp; In this case, while their families have migrated, the couple is young and it is important to understand their background.u003c/liu003entu003cliu003eWhen did they get married?u003c/liu003entu003cliu003eWhy they are not educated?u0026nbsp; To me, it is a bit surprising that the couple is not educated even upto 6th grade.u0026nbsp; Why?u0026nbsp;u003c/liu003entu003cliu003eWhat kind of work do they do?u003c/liu003entu003cliu003ewhat are their day-to-day challenges as a family as well as for the Hemath member?u003c/liu003entu003cliu003ewhat are their aspirations, etc.? why did she join Hemath u0026ndash; what is her expectation and what has happened since she joined Hemath? Lot of these questions remain unanswered.u003c/liu003entu003cliu003eAlso, any thing that is unusual in the earlier sections and cannot be included in those sections should be included in the observations e.g. why there is no savings, why there is no loan, what kind of assistance govt is giving them as they are not paying some of the bills or rent.u003c/liu003enu003c/ulu003ennu003cpu003eu0026nbsp;u0026nbsp;11.u0026nbsp;u003cstrongu003eCommitmentu0026nbsp;u003c/strongu003eu0026ndash; it states u0026ndash; u0026ldquo;yesu0026rdquo; she participates in activities but in describing these activities, It shows u0026ldquo;NAu0026rdquo;.u0026nbsp; Please describe the activities she participates in.u003c/pu003ennu003cpu003ebest, Meenau003c/pu003en
